@{b}Raging Gorilla@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Summon Gorilla (2/3)
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Tom Kyffin

Text(VI): If Raging Gorilla blocks or is blocked, it gets +2/-2 until end
          of turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Every temper tantrum makes another angry gorilla."
