@{b}Relentless Assault@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(R)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 2RR
Artist  = G. Darrow & I. Rabarot

Text(VI): Untap all creatures that attacked this turn. You may declare an
          additional attack during your main phase this turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Flog and Squee
             Up the tree
             See the army
             Flee, flee, flee."
             -Goblin nursery rhyme/war cry@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_R.guide/RELEN}

