@node ROCKS "Rock Slide"

@{b}Rock Slide@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = RX
Artist  = Mike Kerr

Text(VI): Rock slide does X damage, divided any way you choose, among any
          number of target attacking or blocking creatures without flying.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Good ol' rock. Nothing beats rock."
             -Rhirhok, goblin archer@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SOLFA "Solfatara"

@{b}Solfatara@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Omaha P‚rez

Text(VI): Target player cannot play any land cards this turn. Draw a card
          at the beginning of the next turn's upkeep.

Flavor Text: @{i}"A burst of hot air tossed the moon into the air,
             and the moon liked it up there so much it never needed
             the ground again."
             -Azeworai, "Glitter Moon"@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_S.guide/SOLFA}

