@node SONGO "Song of Blood"

@{b}Song of Blood@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 1R
Artist  = Eric Peterson

Text(VI): Put the top four cards from your library into your graveyard.
          For each creature card put into your graveyard in this way, all
          creatures that attack this turn get +1/+0 until end of turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}Purraj sang slaughter and danced death.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_S.guide/SONOB}

