@{b}Spitting Drake@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Summon Drake (2/2)
Cost    = 3R
Artist  = G. Darrow & I. Rabarot

Text(VI): Flying
          <R>: +1/+0 until end of turn. You cannot spend more than <R> in
