@{b}Suq'Ata Lancer@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Summon Knight (2/2)
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Jeff Miracola

Text(VI): Flanking
          Suq'Ata Lancer is unaffected by summoning sickness.

