@{b}Talruum Champion@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Summon Minotaur (3/3)
Cost    = 4R
Artist  = Pete Venters

Text(VI): First Strike.
          Whenever Talruum Champion blocks or is blocked by any creature,
