@{b}Talruum Piper@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Summon Minotaur (3/3)
Cost    = 4R
Artist  = Pete Venters

Text(VI): All creatures with flying able to block Talruum Piper do so.

